From 731265ce95af7e37a398d586549996123d96ba97 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Z User <z@container>
Date: Wed, 1 Jul 2026 00:57:38 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] fix: resolve remaining type-safety, accessibility, DI, and
 schema issues

- H3: Replace all as-unknown-as-Uuid and as-Record casts in products.controller
  with parseUuid() validation and typed ProductResponseDto.fromDomain()
- H10: Replace custom tabs.tsx/scroll-area.tsx with Radix UI primitives
  (keyboard nav, ARIA roles, proper accessibility)
- C6: Add NULL-safe unique index on product_targeting using COALESCE sentinel
- H2b: Make ScoringEngine DI-injectable via useFactory provider
